<h2>Highlights</h2>
<p>
By integrating subscription options into the same form as the regular product options,
Dripkit was able to reduce friction in the shopping process and increase conversions on subscriptions.
Subtle animations on key pages set Dripkit's brand apart from it's competitors.
</p>

