<h3>Personalized Recommendations</h3>
<p>
With the introduction of multiple coffee variations,
we introduced a short quiz for customers to be able to identify which coffee would best fit their tastes,
improving customer satisfaction.
A quiz like this creates the potential for segmenting customers and targeted promotions to better match customer interests.
</p>
